# Advanced Rendering: Using Directives
## DIRECTIVES

- ref
- slotted
- children
- when 
- whenElse
- repeat (as well as c as context object)
- sync


Directives
A. Content & Template Directives

ref (DOM references)
slotted (content projection)
children (child elements)
'c' context object

B. Flow Control Directives

when
whenElse
repeat
sync